[11] Tahiti
Date: Tue 3 Feb 2009
Source: Les Sources de l'Info [in French, trans. Mod.TY, edited]
<http://www.lessourcesdelinfo.info/La-dengue-apparait-a-Tahiti_a3932.html>


Health authorities have reported the official registration of 2 cases of
dengue [virus] type 4. French Polynesia had been so far spared from the
epidemic that has been raging since mid-2008 in several regions of the
South Pacific. The anti-vector effort is to be strengthened. In particular,
people have been asked to eliminate mosquito-breeding sites.

